OL,6,GIs a big shake-up in prospect for the
OL,7,GBBC's two main daytime news
OL,8,Gprogrammes?
OL,10,FThe Times on 3rd June reported plans
OL,11,Ffor a revamp of both Breakfast and
OL,12,Fthe News at One.
OL,14,FIt's understood the idea could see
OL,15,FBreakfast extended to 10am and the
OL,16,FNews at One run for an hour.  The
OL,17,FNews at One would be presented from
OL,18,FSalford.
OL,20,FThe BBC has made no comment on the
OL,21,Fstory.
OL,3,CChanges for BBC Breakfast and BBC
OL,4,CNews at One?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/5
