OL,6,FIt is not inevitable that the changes
OL,7,Fwill go ahead.
OL,9,FBoth programmes get the BBC's biggest
OL,10,Fdaytime ratings. Extending them would
OL,11,Falso mean more bespoke UK content on
OL,12,Fthe News Channel. (The Nicky Campbell
OL,13,Fsimulcast has proved controversial.)
OL,15,FWhat isn't clear is how Breakfast
OL,16,Fwould fill an extra hour.
OL,18,FWould it be more of the same? Or
OL,19,Fmight the extra 45 minutes have its
OL,20,Fown character. Perhaps more regular
OL,21,Ffeatures or lighter interviews?
OL,3,CChanges for BBC Breakfast and BBC
OL,4,CNews at One?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
