OL,6,FMoving the News at One to Salford
OL,7,Fneed not be an issue for viewers.
OL,8,FBreakfast has proved that a national
OL,9,Fnews programme need not be presented
OL,10,Ffrom London.
OL,12,FBut how would the extra time be
OL,13,Ffilled?
OL,15,FAssuming that changes do happen
OL,16,Fthere'd be implications for BBC One's
OL,17,Fdaytime schedule.
OL,3,CChanges for BBC Breakfast and BBC
OL,4,CNews at One?
